data.description: Welcome to 456 Prestwick Ct in the heart of Suntree. This beautiful home is conveniently located across from Suntree Country Club, offering you easy access to its amenities and recreational activities. This distinctive 3-story townhouse boasts a private elevator, providing accessibility to all levels. The recently updated kitchen is sure to impress, featuring modern appliances and ample counter space for meal preparation.  Enjoy low maintenance living with a community pool steps away from your front door. The two-car garage provides secure parking for your vehicles, with additional space available on the driveway for up to four cars. Zoned for top-rated schools, this property offers an ideal setting for families seeking quality education options. New roof installed in 2022.  walking paths and biking trails, this area is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts looking to stay active. The beach, shopping & dining are just a short drive away.  Don't miss out. Schedule your private showing today!
